actions:
- author: oddvar
  body: |-
    oddvar.org is being maintained, but not as an official matrix.org alternative (and AFAIK it's only advertised on the https://matrix.org/blog/project/matrix-console-web/ page). 

    The original intention was to have a list of known clients/servers which could then turn into a "recommended servers" list given that not everyone will/can run their own server. However this is separate to having a "matrix.org" grade alternative server that we commit to maintaining as well as matrix.org
